{
  "title": "GX_SIMULATOR",
  "description": "GX_SIMULATOR is an interactive IDL widget application designed to help researchers construct data-constrained 3D models of solar active regions and flaring loops. The tool supports the generation of spatially resolved radio, X-ray, and EUV spectra based on these models.",
